      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or aging. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine is smooth and powerful, the transmission shifts imperceptibly, and every electronic feature and comfort amenity functions exactly as intended. It has been meticulously maintained with a full service history, making it a rare find for a discerning buyer who demands the highest quality.",
