    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable car at an accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scuffs, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings along the door panels. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all major electronics and climate controls remain functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, but it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It\u2019s a great project car or daily driver for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of cosmetic character.",
