    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, finished in a deep, lustrous factory paint that has been strictly garage-kept and ceramic coated to maintain its mirror-like finish. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery shows zero bolstering wear, and the dashboard remains free of any UV damage or imperfections. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history with every fluid flush and inspection performed ahead of schedule. There are no leaks, no rattles, and the gear transitions are seamless. Included are both original key fobs, the factory window sticker, and all original manuals. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key vehicle that feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
